---
surface: readme_invariant_harness
bead: bd-3usjw.22
schema: ee.closure_surface_golden.v1
purpose: README prose invariants are mechanically extracted and paired with tests.
primary_tests:
  - tests/readme_invariant_harness.rs
  - tests/readme_invariant_manifest_schema.rs
manifest: tests/readme_invariants/manifest.toml
invariants:
  - README candidate sentences with trigger words or numeric units must have manifest coverage.
  - Manifest entries must point to an existing test path or a tracked defer marker.
  - Adding or removing README invariant prose without manifest updates must fail the harness.
verified_by:
  - cargo test --test readme_invariant_harness
  - cargo test --test readme_invariant_manifest_schema

